snippet.title: Pathankot Attack: Gurdaspur SP Salwinder Singh to face a polygraph test

localized.description:
The National Investigation Agency aims to subject Gurdaspur SP Salwinder Singh to a polygraph test to establish the facts regarding the alleged carjacking of his SUV by terrorists who attacked the Pathankot airbase late last week.
